# Ignore LinkedIn and other social media placeholders (using literal strings to avoid regex noise)
https://www.linkedin.com/in/{{
https://twitter.com/{{
https://github.com/{{
https://www.facebook.com/{{
https://www.instagram.com/{{
https://www.linkedin.com/in/%7B%7B

# Ignore 429 (Too Many Requests) from Instagram/LinkedIn
https://www.instagram.com/.*
https://www.linkedin.com/.*

# Ignore specific broken legacy links or non-existent files identified in logs
