https://github.com/academicpages/academicpages.github.io/blob/master/_talks/talkmap.ipynb
https://api.staticman.net/v1/entry/.*

# Ignore placeholder variables that might survive the build (e.g. in JS comments)
\{\{\s*.*\s*\}\}
{%\s*.*\s*%}
